org.cytoscape.search.util
Class AttributeFields

java.lang.Object
  org.cytoscape.search.util.AttributeFields

public class AttributeFields
extends java.lang.Object

This object will serve as input to the CustomMultiFieldQueryParser. It contains attribute fields names and their types. This way CustomMultiFieldQueryParser can recognise numeric attribute fields.
